  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety, pharmacokinetics, and pharmacodynamics
      of NKTT120 in adult patients with stable sickle cell disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
